      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is gone. the funder pulled out, the debt is way more than the remaining assets, and i just... i can't even think about going home. the shame of looking my parents in the eye after all that hype is just too much. i feel like i've reached a dead end where there's literally no way out of this.",
